Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Mababang Paaralan Ng Buenavista in the Municipality of Alabat, Province of Quezon, to Rufina-Tiburcio Camacho Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 505
An Act Changing the Name of the Mababang Paaralan Ng Buenavista in the Municipality of Alabat, Province of Quezon, to Rufina-Tiburcio Camacho Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Mababang Paaralan ng Buenavista in the Municipality of Alabat, Province of Quezon, is changed to Rufina-Tiburcio Camacho Elementary School.1Ã¢wphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: June 10, 1983
